#: ../../source/vuln/pathtraversal.rst:2
msgid "目录穿越"
msgstr "Path Traversal"

#: ../../source/vuln/pathtraversal.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/vuln/pathtraversal.rst:6
msgid ""
"目录穿越（也被称为目录遍历/directory traversal/path traversal）是通过使用 ``../`` "
"等目录控制序列或者文件的绝对路径来访问存储在文件系统上的任意文件和目录，特别是应用程序源代码、配置文件、重要的系统文件等。"
msgstr ""
"Path traversal, also known as directory traversal, accesses arbitrary files "
"and directories stored on the file system by using directory control "
"sequences such as ``../`` or absolute file paths, especially application "
"source code, configuration files, and important system files."

