msgstr "``\\%e0%40%ae``"

#: ../../source/vuln/pathtraversal.rst:36
msgid "防御"
msgstr "Defense"

#: ../../source/vuln/pathtraversal.rst:37
msgid "在进行文件操作相关的API前，应该对用户输入做过滤。较强的规则下可以使用白名单，仅允许纯字母或数字字符等。"
msgstr ""
"Before calling file operation APIs, user input should be filtered. Under "
"stricter rules, use a whitelist that allows only alphabetic or numeric "
"characters."

#: ../../source/vuln/pathtraversal.rst:39
msgid "若规则允许的字符较多，最好使用当前操作系统路径规范化函数规范化路径后，进行过滤，最后再进行相关调用。"
msgstr ""
"If the rules allow a broader set of characters, preferably normalize the "
"path with the current operating system's path normalization function, filter"
" it, and only then perform the related call."

